items.name: Smead 3-in-1 SuperTab Section Folders, Blue, Red, Green, Yellow, 12 / Pack (Quantity)
items.categoryPath: Home Page/Seasonal/Back to School Top Items
items.shortDescription: 3-in-1 SuperTab section folders feature Lockit technology so you can securely subdivide multiple documents within a single file folder. Three extra-high interior pockets safely hold documents, photos and certificates for secure transport while keeping the materials readily accessible. Two pockets are perfect for holding letter-size documents. The second one on the back cover is slightly shorter to hold smaller items and keep them partly visible. All pockets are closed on two sides for easy document insertion. Patented Lockit flap folds over to secure your important documents and prevent them from falling out. The labeling area on the 1/3-cut tab is 90 percent larger than standard file folders so you can use larger text or more lines of description. Folders are made of 11 point stock.Smead 3-in-1 SuperTab Section Folders, Blue, Red, Green, Yellow, 12 / Pack (Quantity)
